border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">关于爱情，其实很多问题都相似，例如：</span></p><p style=\"margin: 0px 32px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; clear: both; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(63, 63, 63); font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 0.5px; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"/></span></p><ul class=\" list-paddingleft-2\" helvetica=\"\" hiragino=\"\" sans=\"\" microsoft=\"\" font-size:=\"\" white-space:=\"\" style=\"margin-right: 32px; margin-left: 32px; width: 530.094px; padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal;\"><li><p style=\"padding: 0px; clear: both;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(63, 63, 63); font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 0.5px; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">为什么我总遇不到对的人？</span></p></li><li><p style=\"padding: 0px; clear: both;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(63, 63, 63); font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 0.5px; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">怎样判断Ta是不是合适我？</span></p></li><li><p style=\"padding: 0px; clear: both;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(63, 63, 63); font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 0.5px; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">为什么在爱中我时常感到不安？</span></p></li><li><p style=\"padding: 0px; clear: both;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(63, 63, 63); font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 0.5px; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">谈恋爱应该找性格相似